93.8	Lars_von_Trier	Lars von Trier	Lars von Trier (Danish pronunciation: ; born Lars Trier; 30 April 1956) is a Danish film director and screenwriter. He is closely associated with the Dogme 95 collective — an avant-garde filmmaking movement — although his own films have taken a variety of approaches. His work has frequently divided the critics.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/67/LarsVonTrier.jpg/220px-LarsVonTrier.jpg
